    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/9428643af19d5790c6805911f60f9375.avif?t=1742554671\" width=450 height=253 /></span>。<br><br>整理背包》是一款轻松的益智游戏，您必须将背包中找到的奇幻战利品整理得整整齐齐。找到被遗忘的文物，了解旧世界的细节......至少应该是这样！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能[/h2］[list］<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>96个手工制作的关卡<br></li><li>33件独特物品<br></li><li>轻松的游戏玩法<br></li><li>操作简单<br></li><li>舒适的图形<br></li><li>轻松的音乐</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事[/h2］找到几千年前的物品，把它们装进你整洁的背包里，看看它们在旧世界的用途。不过，现在我们只能猜测这些文物的用途......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/12699845e5ff239ab90a0ecc88f1599d.poster.avif?t=1742554671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/12699845e5ff239ab90a0ecc88f1599d.webm?t=1742554671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/12699845e5ff239ab90a0ecc88f1599d.mp4?t=1742554671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法[/h2］1. 按住左键抓取物品<br>2. 右键单击旋转<br>3. 将一个楼层的所有物品装入背包<br>4. 享受您的完美搭配！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/58bf7eed5d38b5e1c61e20856e45f179.poster.avif?t=1742554671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/58bf7eed5d38b5e1c61e20856e45f179.webm?t=1742554671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047220/extras/58bf7eed5d38b5e1c61e20856e45f179.mp4?t=1742554671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2></h2></h2>",
